<span id="freeTextContainer861689207441821008">I read this book in two days; I just could not put it down. I&apos;m not usually one for Western Romance Novels but I got hooked on this one. Such interesting characters a duchess and a Cheyenne Warrior, combine that with a great story and the steamy love scenes, who could resist. I also enjoyed the fact that the leading lady wasn&apos;t some push over; she was spunky and could hold her own. Johanna Lindsey you have not let me down yet. </span>
